        <p style="font-size:40px; font-family: Arial; font-weight:bold;">WHAT WE DO</p>
            <p style="font-size:17px; font-family: Arial; font-weight:bold;">Save A Pet Florida, Inc. was originally founded as “Save Precious Lives, Inc.” by Gertrude Maxwell in 1978.  The name was changed to Save A Pet Florida, Inc. on January 19, 1988. Every day our volunteers donate their time to rescue homeless animals from a parking lot, a car engine, an abandoned building, etc.</p>
